<Base title="About — Cosmos Research" description="About the Cosmos Research Center.">
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    Cosmos Research Center is a multi-generational platform for exploring science, ideas, and the
    big questions — from the Hubble tension to human vitality.
  </p>
  <p>
    We believe great science happens when curiosity is given room to breathe. This site is a home
    for essays, computational experiments, research notes, and the kind of slow thinking that
    doesn't fit neatly into a conference paper.
  </p>
  <h2>People</h2>
  <p>
    <strong>Tom Munnecke</strong> — founder, systems thinker, and lifelong explorer of what makes
    things work.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Abigail</strong> — next-generation researcher bringing fresh eyes to old problems.
  </p>
</Base>
